  "game": {
    "title": "ONLY UP!",
    "description": "Embark on an exhilarating journey in Only Up!, where the only way is up! Test your precision, patience, and platforming skills as you navigate towering obstacles, floating platforms, and unpredictable pathways to reach the highest heights. Every step is a challenge, every jump is a risk, and one wrong move could send you tumbling back down.\nWith realistic physics, immersive visuals, and a thrilling sense of vertical exploration, Only Up! offers an intense and rewarding experience for those who dare to climb. How far can you go before gravity catches up with you?\nKey Features:\n- Climb to the Top – Conquer a massive vertical world filled with unique obstacles.\n- Precision & Timing – Every movement matters. Stay focused or fall!\n- Dynamic Environments – Experience a surreal world with floating islands, twisting paths, and unpredictable terrain.\n- Skill-Based Gameplay – No shortcuts, just pure challenge and mastery.\n-No Limits – How high can you reach before making a mistake?\nTake a deep breath, take a leap, and begin your climb in Only Up! – a true test of patience and skill!",
